title: Putin reviews Russia's 'invincible weapons' during military parade
text:
Putin reviews Russia's 'invincible weapons' during military parade 8:57am EDT - 00:50
Russia shows off its military might during an annual parade, including a hypersonic missile President Vladimir Putin has touted as invincible Rough cut (no reporter narration).
